| TypeScript 5.7+                | Language (strict mode, ES2022, ESM, Node16 module resolution) |
| Vitest 3                       | Test framework                                                |
| ESLint 9 + typescript-eslint 8 | Linting (flat config)                                         |
| Node.js 18+                    | Runtime                                                       |

